Repost• Advantages to wear designer dresses on rent
@srishtisehgaldesigns 
@rentanattirevilla 
📷 @pihufilms_photography 

1.Saves your money
If you decide to rent clothes it can be convenient and cost effective way to shop. Renting also improves the risk of impulse buying.

2.Save wardrobe space
If you rent clothes you will obviously  find that you free up a lot of space in wardrobe- after a good sort of course.

3.You will never run out of clothes you wear
It’s quite often people don’t want to wear same thing over and over again. So, renting your outfits gives you an endless supply of outfits without the guilt of only wearing something else.

4.New look
You can try out a new style that you wouldn’t normally go for without fear of wasting money on something that you wouldn’t wear again.

5.Renting saves your time
A one-stop marketplace where you can browse through dresses for every occasion and then have it delivered straight to your address is never a time consuming task.
